{"tid":882650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"周綺萍：恆管升格畢業生入職薪金可升10%","createTime":"2018-10-30T09:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T00:21:55.000Z","uid":41404,"like":12,"dislike":186,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"3dfdf4cca9fad979df1927158398fefe9660e632","tid":882650,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:34:59.000Z","msg":"行政會議今日正式通過恒生管理學院升格為大學，安俊人力資源顧問董事總經理周綺萍表示，恒管的工商管理課程在商界有不俗的口碑，不少僱主都願意聘請恒管畢業生，相信正名後對學生日後搵工幫助更大，入職薪金可望上升5至10%。<br />\n<br />\n周綺萍表示，恒管獲正名為大學，等同進行一步確認有關學院的學術水平，「學院就係學院，同大學始終有唔同」。除了入職薪金有別，學院正名後也有助增加學生的晉升機會，「有啲職位寫到明要大學畢業，如果你冇大學資歷，上司要升你嘅時候，要申請豁免，但依傢就唔使。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181030/58853551\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181030%2F58853551&d=%2Bi4EYpcX0ygC0tY6g2C%2Fs26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=f851509a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181030%2F58853551&h=e36e7176\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181030/58853551</a>"},{"pid":"0178c887103978e680a782462d59d9bdb09cddbc","tid":882650,"uid":189053,"like":162,"dislike":2,"score":160,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:37:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6fb1c9e053e098e2f93324a58a3fc79e743192d0","tid":882650,"uid":53421,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:38:04.000Z","msg":"含大含大"},{"pid":"e4fd391c4143a19968e144e51bea69dd11fec979","tid":882650,"uid":810,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:38:29.000Z","msg":"貢撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec80f67284b136f7b0d96d89d38173f651d8c11","tid":882650,"uid":102096,"like":33,"dislike":3,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:39:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e796fe6d9eb84137ea1987905eccb221780c334c","tid":882650,"uid":